claim.claim-text:
1. A light emitting device package comprising:
a substrate;
an electrode layer on the substrate;
a light emitting device on the substrate and electrically connected to the electrode layer;
a molding part surrounding the light emitting device and comprising protrusions; and
a photoresist layer disposed only on the protrusions of the molding part,
wherein the molding part and the photoresist layer form the protrusions having high points and low points, the photoresist layer being only on the high points.
